definitions.definition: A numerical value equal to 100 (10 ), occurring after ninety-nine .
examples: A few hundred pounds' worth of chicken and serveral dozen eggs.

definitions.definition: The pronunciation of “00” for the two digits denoting the minutes.

main_definition: A numerical value equal to 100 (10 ), occurring after ninety-nine .
secondary_definitions: ( 24-hour clock ) The pronunciation of “00” for the two digits denoting the minutes.
